headline: From Campus to Career: Hormel Foods Welcomes 95 Interns for Transformative Summer Experience
summary: It's more than an internship — it's a launchpad to a rewarding career. Typically, more than 70% of Hormel Foods interns become full-time team members at the company. Starting today, the company will welcome over 95 students from 50 colleges and universities across the country.
